OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FPolice officers ordered to 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fshave off beards           
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Police Scotland is planning to         
OL,6, introduce a new clean-shaven policy for
OL,7, frontline officers, according to       
OL,8, correspondence seen by the BBC.        
OL,10,FIt means hundreds of officers will have
OL,11,Fto shave off their beards and          
OL,12,Fmoustaches by the end of the month.    
OL,14,FFour are understood to be taking legal 
OL,15,Faction in relation to the policy.      
OL,17,FPolice Scotland said it was necessary  
OL,18,Fso officers and staff could wear       
OL,19,Fprotective FFP3 masks which require    
OL,20,Fusers to be clean-shaven.              
